Ƙungiyar ta lissafa matsakaicin farashin kuɗi a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Wannan ba shi da kyau kamar sauran tashoshin watsa labarai na yanzu, PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
