Ri Yong Ho ya bayyana a taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta gudanar da muhimman ayyukan kirki a shekarar da ta gabata, a halin yanzu don kawo karshen gwajin makaman nukiliya da makamai masu linzami, kawar da tashar binciken nukiliya, da kuma ba da yabo ga kada a kara yawan makaman nukiliya.
Sai ya ce, "Amma ba mu sami irin wannan amsa daga Amurka ba".
