Paul Barreira, malamin ilimin halayyar dan adam a Harvard Medical School kuma shugaban jami'ar kiwon lafiya, ya ce jami'ar ta zabi ta gabatar da wannan shirin bayan ta lura cewa dalibai suna fama da rashin bacci.
