Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya nuna ranar Lahadi da ta gabata ga jaridar China Daily mai suna Des Moines Register - jaridar da ta fi kowa sayarwa a jihar Iowa - bayan ya zargi kasar Sin da kokarin neman takararsa a majalisar wakilai a Amurka a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da kasar ta musanta.
